(1049, 'VIASPACE John Hatsopoulos, Thermo Electron Co-Founder And Former President  & CFO, Joins VIASPACE Board', '', '\r\n<P class=MsoBodyTextIndent style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">PASADENA, CA?February 15, 2006 ?VIASPACE Inc. (OTCBB: VSPC)</SPAN>, <SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt">a company that transforms proven space and defense technologies from NASA and the Department of Defense </SPAN>into hardware and software solutions, <SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt">announced today</SPAN> the addition of John N. Hatsopoulos <SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">to its Board of Directors. </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 9.5pt">This appointment brings the total number of Company directors to six.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Mr. </SPAN>Hatsopoulos <SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 9.5pt">is the Company?s third independent director</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">.</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyTextIndent style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyTextIndent style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in"><FONT face=Verdana size=2>John N. Hatsopoulos is chief executive officer of American Distributed Generation Inc. headquartered in Waltham, Massachusetts.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>He is also chairman of GlenRose Capital LLC, a leveraged buyout investment fund, and a managing partner of Alexandros Partners LLC, a financial advisory firm. Previously, for a tenure of 42 years, Mr. Hatsopoulos was co-founder, vice chairman, president, and chief financial officer, of Thermo Electron Corporation, a leading provider of analytical and monitoring instruments used in a broad range of applications. In these positions, he implemented numerous financial strategies that became the focus of worldwide interest, including his spinout strategy, which resulted in 24 public companies. Mr. Hatsopoulos was also integral in helping Thermo Electron and its subsidiaries raise more than $5 billion of capital. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0.5in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>Mr. Hatsopoulos graduated from Athens College in Athens, Greece, in 1953. He holds a B.S. in history and mathematics from Northeastern University, together with Honorary Doctorates in Business Administration from Boston College and Northeastern University.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>He served on the Board of Directors of the American Stock Exchange from 1994 through 2000. He is currently a member of the Board of Directors of TEI BioSciences Inc., and a ?Member of the Corporation? for Northeastern University. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-highlight: yellow"><o:p><FONT face=Verdana size=2></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>Dr. Carl Kukkonen, Chief Executive Officer of VIASPACE, said, ?<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">VIASPACE is honored to have John Hatsopoulos join our Board as an independent director. While President and CFO of Thermo Electron, Mr. Hatsopoulos was instrumental in growing two dozen of the company?s subsidiaries into successful businesses that subsequently went public on their own. His strategic advice and vast business and financial experience will be invaluable to VIASPACE.?<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><B><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2><B>About VIASPACE</B>: Unparalleled Knowledge.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Unparalleled Solutions.</FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT face=Verdana size=2>VIASPACE is a diversified technology company with knowledge and expertise in energy/fuel cells, microelectronics, sensors, homeland security and public safety, and information and computational technology. Founded in 1998 with the objective of transforming proven space and defense technologies<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana"> </SPAN>from NASA and the Department of Defense into hardware and software solutions that solve today''s complex problems, VIASPACE benefits from important patent and software licenses from Caltech, which manages NASA?s Jet Propulsion Laboratory, and from relationships with research laboratories, universities, and other organizations within the advanced technology community.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>For more information, please visit our website at </FONT><A href="http://www.viaspace.com/"><FONT face=Verdana size=2>www.VIASPACE.com</FONT></A><FONT face=Verdana size=2>, or contact Investor Relations at (888) 359-9558, or </FONT><A href="mailto:IR@VIASPACE.com"><FONT face=Verdana size=2>IR@VIASPACE.com</FONT></A><FONT face=Verdana size=2>, or Publi