(1477, 'VIASPACE CEO Provides Update On Nicaragua Giant King® Grass Plantation and 12 MW Power Plant at International Biomass Conference', '', '<font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="3">May 12, 2015 - Walnut, </font><font size="3">California</font><font size="3"> - </font><span style="color: black"><font size="3">VIASPACE Inc. (OTC: VSPC) announced that VIASPACE CEO, Dr. Carl Kukkonen, made a presentation at the International Biomass Conference and Expo held April 20-22, 2015 in Minneapolis, Minnesota. The presentation provided a case study and update on the 12 MW biomass power plant and 2,100 acre Giant King Grass plantation project being developed in Nicaragua.</font><span><font size="3">&nbsp; </font></span></span></font></p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify"><span style="color: black"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify"><span style="color: black"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">The eighth annual International Biomass Conference and Expo attracted 1,400 industry professionals and 204 exhibitors from all sectors of the world&rsquo;s biomass utilization industries&mdash;biobased power, thermal energy, biogas, biofuels and biochemicals.</font></span></p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify"><span style="color: black"><br /><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"> Dr. Kukkonen&rsquo;s presentation included an overview of the project and its status which is summarized below.</font></span></p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify"><span style="color: black"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">  </fo