(50, 'Deep Domain Expertise', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">In addition to the experience and abilities of its internal team, VIASPACE benefits from the domain expertise of leading experts serving on its scientific and business advisory boards, its teaming partners, and an informal global network of respected researchers, technology analysts, engineers and investors.</span></p>', 1, 50),
