(100, '2. What are VIASPACE''s subsidiaries?', 'The company has three operating subsidiaries. Direct Methanol Fuel Cell Corportation (DMFCC) operates within the VIASPACE Energy Division.&nbsp; VIASPACE Security Inc. and Ionfinity LLC operate in the VIASPACE Security division.', 1, 100),
(101, '3. When and where was VIASPACE formed?', 'VIASPACE&rsquo;s predecessor company, ViaSpace Technologies LLC was formed under the laws of Delaware in 1998. In June 2005, ViaSpace Technologies LLC merged into Global-Wide Publication, Ltd., a corporation formed under the laws of Nevada, and changed its name to VIASPACE Inc.', 1, 101),
(102, '4. Where is VIASPACE located?', 'VIASPACE&rsquo;s executive offices are at 171 N Altadena Dr. in Pasadena California, a Los Angeles suburb where Caltech and NASA/JPL are located.', 1, 102),
(103, '5. Who is VIASPACE''s management team?', '<a href="management_team.php">Click here</a>  for management biographies.', 1, 103),
(104, '6. Where does VIASPACE''s stock trade?', 'VIASPACE&rsquo;s stock currently trades on the Over the Counter Bulletin Board under the symbol VSPC (OTCBB: VSPC).', 1, 104),
(105, '7. What is VIASPACE?s capital structure?', 'The authorized capital of VIASPACE is 800,000,000 shares of common stock and 5,000,000 shares of preferred stock. ', 1, 105),
(107, '8. In what industries does VIASPACE operate and provide solutions?', 'Homeland security, public safety, risk assessment and decision support for port security, Seaport cargo and truck inspection, counter-terrorism, supply chain management and tracking of physical assets, continuous tracking of emergency personnel and other first responders in hazardous environments, and providing longer-lasting, efficient power for laptops, cell phones, and other portable electronic devices.', 1, 107),
(108, '9. When is VIASPACE''s year-end?', 'VIASPACE&#39;s fiscal year ends December 31.', 1, 108),
(109, '10. When will VIASPACE announce financial results?', 'VIASPACE generally reports its financial results six weeks after the close of the quarter in interim quarters and 12 weeks following the close of its year-end. ', 1, 109),
(111, '11. How can I be added to VIASPACE''s distribution list for press releases and other company information by e-mail?', 'To receive VIASPACE press releases, email investor relations at <a href="mailto:IR@VIASPACE.com">IR@VIASPACE.com</a> with your request.', 1, 111),
(113, '12. Does VIASPACE offer a direct purchase plan for shares of company stock?', 'The company does not offer a direct purchase plan at this time. If you would like to purchase VIASPACE stock, please contact your brokerage firm.', 1, 113),
